    "Id": "chassisdef_battlecat_BTC-6N",
    "Name": "Battlecat",
    "Details": "The BTC-6N pairs a Rotary AC/5 and twin Streak SRM 4s with a Targeting Computer for reliable direct combat output across ranges. Two Medium Pulse Lasers add close-range bite, while a Mech Mortar 4 with shaped-charge ammunition bypasses Anti-Missile Systems entirely and can swap to smoke or airburst rounds as the situation demands. The combination gives Canopian commanders unusual tactical flexibility in a single 75-ton frame.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
    "Icon": "NEEDS_ICON"
