  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "Majesty Metals built this one specifically for the MAF, and you can tell they were thinking about real battlefield problems. The mortar is the interesting part. Most people overlook it but it punches through AMS coverage that would stop anything else you could put in that slot. Saw some of these deployed to Cate's Hold after the pirate attack there. Solid, dependable machine. Nothing flashy, just gets the job done.",
